title: O'NEILL PSYCHO 1 2013/14
description: The Psycho 1 is minimal seam madness and is now available in youth sizes. This suit is the ultimate high-performance cold-water wetsuit. The Psycho 1 is built with Ultra gooey TechnoButter Neoprene and ultra-minimal seam styling, which offers unrestricted mobility, enhanced durability and incredible fit. The Psycho 1 will raise your performance level to new heights and will let you "Surf Lighter, Surf Longer".
